item.title: 2 Problems Help Plz!
item.dc:creator: @bryanc Bryanc
item.description:
@bryanc wrote:

You need an opening bracket:

if(command.startsWith("varrock")) { teleportToX = 3213; teleportToY = 3423; sendMessage("Welcome To New Varrock Designed By Sean!"); }

For portals, get the portal Id.

Make a case ##: with the portal id replacing ‘##’.
Put the case with the other case’s, and more specifically with other portal cases.
Add a portal the way a portal is already added… if you don’t have any portals, then I cannot help ya. I don’t use globalObjects.
